{"tid":1907133,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐洲安道爾 葡萄牙 確診首宗支那肺炎","createTime":"2020-03-02T11:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T17:10:36.000Z","uid":223664,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"84375248d11d64838c222dde234c5ba5544b79c9","tid":1907133,"uid":223664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T11:45:21.000Z","msg":"（中央社里斯本2日綜合外電報導）葡萄牙電視台SIC報導，葡萄牙今天通報該國首宗2起武漢肺炎感染病例。<br />\n<br />\nSIC報導，其中一例是一名最近到義大利旅遊的男子，另一例則是一名從西班牙返國的男子。兩人都已送到波圖（Porto）的醫院治療。<br />\n<br />\n葡萄牙衛生部官員未能立即聯繫上對此置評。（譯者：陳正健/核稿：劉淑琴）1090302<br />\n-----<br />\n歐洲小國安道爾政府今天宣布，一名最近曾造訪義大利的20歲男子出現新冠肺炎輕微症狀，是安道爾首例確診患者。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報導，這名男子最近去過米蘭，2月29日入院接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n安道爾政府在聲明中表示，這名患者檢驗結果呈陽性，將留院做進一步檢測，並將監控他最密切接觸的社交圈。<br />\n<br />\n2020-03-02 19:24 中央社 / 馬德里2日綜合外電報導"},{"pid":"f529bf2548af9eff0f8f9d6e60ee1fdcf301a4df","tid":1907133,"uid":223664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T11:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a992df1ffd8d5685fb7b2c99b590b18a11886e","tid":1907133,"uid":223664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T11:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f54d10daa3bb919d93e92b2e296b5aa5667566","tid":1907133,"uid":51200,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T11:47:09.000Z","msg":"安道爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713ab83ed7d7eeb530e79871c7e093bde36db198","tid":1907133,"uid":212646,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T11:48:04.000Z","msg":"連愛爾蘭同北愛咁少支那人都有，你覺得歐洲有國家可以獨善其身咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c44203ca19c072ca4b8f9f176dc100c32780